high_descs: Turn right, move towards the bath, then turn left and move towards the black table.
Pick up the soap bar near the front right corner of the table.
Turn around and move towards and face the sink.
Place the soap bar in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and pick up the soap bar from the sink.
Turn right, move forward toward the toilet, turn left and face the rubbish bin to the right of the sink.
Place the bar of soap into the rubbish bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned soap bar into a rubbish bin.

high_descs: Turn right towards the bath tub.
Turn left when at bath tub.
Pick up pink soap on desk near bath tub.
Turn left, turn left again towards sink.
Place soap into sink, turn sink on, turn off when done.
Turn right, place soap into garbage near toilet.
anns.task_desc: Pick up soap, use it, throw into trash.

high_descs: Move to the black table next to the tub.
Pick up the soap on the right of the table.
Bring the soap to the sink.
Put the soap in the sink, wet the soap with water, pick up the soap from the sink.
Bring the soap to the green trash can.
Put the soap in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put the right soap in the trash can.
